    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“电子市场模拟器”是一款冷静的第一人称模拟游戏，包含运行电子市场的每个细节。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>商店管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/03d042ec23909d344decddb1af694933.poster.avif?t=1765906754\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/03d042ec23909d344decddb1af694933.webm?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/03d042ec23909d344decddb1af694933.mp4?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将您的商店设计得美观且高效。确定产品的展示位置、管理货架并通过提高客户满意度来提供完美的购物体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>供应货物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/d3c5da181c3463500faf3fd3c261b916.poster.avif?t=1765906754\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/d3c5da181c3463500faf3fd3c261b916.webm?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/d3c5da181c3463500faf3fd3c261b916.mp4?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用游戏内的计算机订购物品。根据您的意愿将产品放置在您的商店中并将其提供给您的客户。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>收银员</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/01ce116350873969daa8f8b6c7e2e005.poster.avif?t=1765906754\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/01ce116350873969daa8f8b6c7e2e005.webm?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/01ce116350873969daa8f8b6c7e2e005.mp4?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过收银机移动物品并通过现金或信用卡收取付款。雇用额外的收银员以提高客户满意度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级您的商店</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/ab56c6dd34444428d7eb696218117699.poster.avif?t=1765906754\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/ab56c6dd34444428d7eb696218117699.webm?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/ab56c6dd34444428d7eb696218117699.mp4?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好后升级您的建筑；添加更多收银员以提高销售速度，让您的商店更上一层楼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在线订单</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/76a966741aa082e52a670850263daef5.poster.avif?t=1765906754\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/76a966741aa082e52a670850263daef5.webm?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/76a966741aa082e52a670850263daef5.mp4?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过跟踪在线订单，将您的产品送达客户。您行动得越快，就能越快赚钱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>设置价格</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/5cf904dae9e75243db90069b659732b8.poster.avif?t=1765906754\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/5cf904dae9e75243db90069b659732b8.webm?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041550/extras/5cf904dae9e75243db90069b659732b8.mp4?t=1765906754\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赚钱、升级并扩大您的商店。然后通过租用新商店来增加收入。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>客户满意度和价格政策对于在“电子市场模拟器”游戏中取得成功非常重要。通过做出正确的决定并增加商店数量，您能否赢得这场竞赛，登上城市之巅？</strong></p>",
